            Techniciens certifiés Certibiocide, respect des normes et protection des occupants et des biens.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-neutral-600 space-y-1">
            <li>• Certification Certibiocide obligatoire</li>
            <li>• Équipements de protection (EPI)</li>
            <li>• Intervention en milieux sensibles</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Transparence -->
        <div class="service-card text-center">
          <div class="service-icon bg-premium-500 mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/>
            </svg>
